{"tid":2066318,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"裝修工人撕連儂牆文宣襲擊兩市民　判囚10個月","createTime":"2020-06-16T08:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T08:30:36.000Z","uid":54800,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1afa07516acf1801aad6c23f9bb7efb9c097fc50","tid":2066318,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:06:49.000Z","msg":"一名男子去年7月撕毀連儂牆的文宣及便利貼時被一名青年制止，男子其後奪去青年的雨傘、扯對方眼鏡，並用雨傘毆打對方，更將另一名市民的頭撞向牆。<br />\n<br />\n報稱是裝修工人的34歲被告張俊延，早前承認刑毀及傷人等4項罪名，案件在觀塘裁判法院判刑，裁判官拒絕接納被告因酒醉而打人，指事主沒有作出挑釁，卻遭被告打傷，判被告監禁10個月，並須向事主賠償350元。<br />\n<br />\n案發在去年7月24日，被告在牛頭角通往坪石邨的行人隧道內，非法及惡意傷害及襲擊兩名事主，並損壞一把雨傘及一副眼鏡。"},{"pid":"1311ed0fbce8c79ca2b5ab89b048eb77cc833042","tid":2066318,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:10:18.000Z","msg":"法國好多案都係判10個月.....<br />\n有一單竟然係吐口水襲警.....10個月...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f982f94e908b098410c23fb03ab32b47cb7358c","tid":2066318,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:13:37.000Z","msg":"350元<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390530d16968f46e7a604b0bb61a7bcbfdaf295f","tid":2066318,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7N4Y7FY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7N4Y7FY.gif&h=cc0ea304&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a48bc5532f01307f1746b9a9041cd1df2236f3e","tid":2066318,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"390530d16968f46e7a604b0bb61a7bcbfdaf295f","tid":2066318,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7N4Y7FY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7N4Y7FY.gif&h=cc0ea304&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:16:07.000Z","msg":"唔係哩單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2